<example id="example" otherprops="examples"><title>Example</title>
      <p>In the following code sample, a figure is used to associate a title and a description with
        an image.</p>
      <codeblock>&lt;fig&gt;
&lt;title&gt;The handshake&lt;/title&gt;
&lt;desc&gt;This image shows two hands clasped in a formal, 
business-like handshake.&lt;/desc&gt;
&lt;image href="59j0p66.jpg"&gt;
 &lt;alt&gt;A handshake&lt;/alt&gt;
&lt;/image&gt;
&lt;/fig&gt;</codeblock></example>
